metadata.name: Ukrainian women
metadata.description:
This is women in Ukrainian national clothes. 7 days ago we were gonna drive our kids to schools, go to work, grow our businesses, visit our mothers.
Now, Ukrainian women are giving birth in bomb shelters, trying their best to stay calm and to calm their kids. 
Participating in fights, preparing Molotovs cocktails, volunteering, putting their lives at risk by saving other people.

Together we stand strong!
